data.name: label7.Text
data.value:
This option allows you to port TWRP custom recovery to your device. While this is designed for AMLogic devices, it still will work with other devices. If pulling recovery from a device that is not AMlogic, be sure to change the block path to the correct path.
Select your stock recovery to get started or connect device and choose to pull it from the device. We do the rest!

data.name: label10.Text
data.value:
This option allows you to flash roms automatcally. Your device must be fully booted and rooted to be able to do this. We push the zip to device and tailor TWRP ORS to install the .zip. We then reboot into recovery and the ORS automatically flashes the rom and reboots
